**		22-apr-88 (kenl)
**			Added GLOBALDEF of allow_updates (used to indicate
**			if any keys were found for tables).
**		23-nov-88 (kenl)
**			Added GLOBALDEF of allow_appends.  From IBM group (ham).
**		03-mar-89 (kenl) bug #4876
